  "keyFeatures": [
    "ClickHouse-backed time-series data platform",
    "SnQL and MQL query languages with graph logical data model",
    "Multi-dataset support for independent data partitions",
    "Rule-based query optimizer for efficient ClickHouse queries",
    "Direct Kafka ingestion with consumer framework",
    "Migration system for DDL changes in single-node and distributed environments",
    "Point-in-time and streaming queries (subscriptions)",
    "Admin web interface for managing queries, migrations, and system state"
